name: Holoeyes Edu
summary: New medical education platform "Holoeyes Edu" by VR  <Three features of Holoeyes Edu> 1. Understanding human anatomy, techniques, and techniques in 3D space with VR 2. Anyone can create original VR teaching materials by recording the movement and voice of 3D model data in a three-dimensional space. 3. User's learning behavior history can be acquired Visualize the effect on understanding and grades by utilizing VR
